<span class="displaytext">chicago, il - today senator (candidate last) made the following statement on the contract agreement between verizon communications inc., communications workers of america, and the international brotherhood of electrical workers. <p>"i want to congratulate verizon, cwa and ibew for reaching an agreement that will provide tens of thousands of workers with the good pay, health care, and benefits they deserve. and i want to commend verizon for recognizing the good work that union members can do for their company." </p></span>



